{"tid":1092750,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"$2450超清爽「牛仔底褲」","createTime":"2019-04-05T05:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T09:58:07.000Z","uid":228995,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c0e701f4fed40c1852e1252caa16034ebaef7a47","tid":1092750,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:54:02.000Z","msg":"//牛仔褲是百搭的時尚服飾，炎熱的夏天很多人都會穿上牛仔熱褲。這幾年牛仔褲愈出愈短，有比利時品牌Y/Project近日就推出比熱褲更短的牛仔褲──牛仔內褲，引起網民討論。<br />\n<br />\n從網站「SSENSE」可見，比利時品牌Y/Project推出的牛仔內褲售$2450一條，內褲為100%純棉製造，布料硬挺厚實，經過褪色處理並有3個口袋。模特穿起來就如內褲一樣，甚至會露出少許屁股，非常性感，同時對穿著者的身材要求極高，超級容易露出身材缺點。內褲暫設有兩色，一款是經典的藍色，另一款是黑色。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2315000/2318488/D2mQjOnXcAAeKB9_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2315000%2F2318488%2FD2mQjOnXcAAeKB9_1024.jpg&h=9f75ca11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2315000/2318488/ssense_54512648_389971428509069_24797209087936897_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2315000%2F2318488%2Fssense_54512648_389971428509069_24797209087936897_n_1024.jpg&h=257097bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7be2f85ad9a03676875b0fd456885231a7f2c05","tid":1092750,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0316f74f3794643d8b84d64592676b7d9a6145f9","tid":1092750,"uid":172798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49565d5efde6f2a93e490f44b17b832a4c836e9","tid":1092750,"uid":9411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e3c436